<a name="rsafaq">
RSA Laboratories.
<cite>Frequently Asked Questions about Today's Cryptography.</cite>
Version 4.1. May 2000.  
<a href="rsalabs_faq41.pdf"><b>(pdf---with internal links)</b></a>
</a>
<p>
<a href="http://catless.ncl.ac.uk/Risks/"><b>The Risks Digest</b></a>
<p>  
<a href="http://www.securityfocus.com/"><b>SecurityFocus</b></a>
(where BugTraq comes from)
<p>
<a href="http://www.cert.org/"><b>CERT</b></a>
(US gov't-funded security response center at CMU)
